    "), API usage, and calling context.",
    "This capability of LLMs can be harnessed to create test cases, specifically generating inputs targeting branch conditions that necessitate particular input values or states.",
    "However, when tasked with generating test inputs for methods with challenging or complex branch conditions, LLMs usually succeed in producing inputs for the easy branches, leaving behind the branches with more complex conditions.",
